  "prompt": "What hotel in Firozabad would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "When looking for a hotel in Firozabad that is safe for unmarried couples, consider opting for well-rated establishments that are known for their policies accommodating couples. Here are a few tips to find a suitable option:\n\n1. **Check Online Reviews**: Look for hotels that have positive reviews regarding their treatment of unmarried couples on platforms like TripAdvisor, Google Reviews, or MakeMyTrip.\n\n2. **Couple-Friendly Hotels**: Some hotel chains and online booking platforms allow you to filter for \"couple-friendly\" or \"unmarried couples allowed\" options. \n\n3. **Reputable Brands**: Consider established hotel brands known for their more liberal policies, which might be more understanding toward unmarried couples.\n\n4. **Direct Communication**: Contact the hotel directly to inquire about their policies on unmarried couples before making a reservation. \n\nSome potential options to consider are:\n- **Hotel Sapphire**: Known for good service and accommodating policies.\n- **Hotel Ganga View**: Check their reviews and policies regarding unmarried couples.\n\nAlways ensure to book through reputable channels and to clarify any concerns with the staff prior to your arrival.",
